ecent experiments this firms up the best estimate of\n$0.0075\\pm0.0021 M_{\\odot} {\\rm pc^{-3}}$ ($0.28\\pm0.08 {\\rm GeV cm^{-3}} $),\nconsistent with global fits of approximately round dark matter halos to\nkinematic data in the outskirts of the Galaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Sep 2012 07:05:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 31 May 2013 01:46:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
