on by dust is present in all\ngalaxies, the most extreme case being III Zw 102. Our data reveal a manifold of\nkinematical patterns, from overall regular gas and stellar rotation to complex\nvelocity fields produced by structurally and kinematically distinct components.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Sep 2012 11:24:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
